A4.text: Newsom was elected governor of California in 2018 and reelected in 2022.

A5.text: On February 11, 2015, Newsom announced that he was opening a campaign account for governor in the 2018 elections, allowing him to raise funds for a campaign to succeed Brown as governor of California.
